      "content": "it just feels so exhausting though. like, if everything is just a temporary experience that eventually gets erased, the struggle to \"grow\" or \"learn\" feels like a massive waste of energy. why keep holding on to a life that doesn't actually matter? if there's no ultimate reason to be here, wouldn't it be more logical to just stop fighting the void?",
